---
---
<section id="demos" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-20 fade-in">
      <div class="badge mb-5">See it in action</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary tracking-tight mb-5">
        Real conversations.<br/><span class="text-cal-gold">Not scripted.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
        These are actual interactions showing how OpenMind handles coursework, career advice, and campus life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Demo 1: Skill gap analysis — full width, flagship feature -->
    <div class="terminal mb-8 fade-in shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div>
        <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-text-muted font-sans">openmind &mdash; skill gap analysis</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body space-y-4 text-[13px] md:text-sm">
        <div>
          <span class="text-text-muted">You &rarr;</span>
          <span class="text-text-primary"> What skills am I missing for AI PM roles?</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Based on your resume and your goal of becoming an AI PM:
          <br/><br/>
          <span class="text-green-500">&check;</span> <span class="text-text-primary">Strong</span>: Python, ML fundamentals, NLP, data analysis<br/>
          <span class="text-green-500">&check;</span> <span class="text-text-primary">Strong</span>: Technical communication (from your BAIR research)
          <br/><br/>
          <span class="text-yellow-500">&triangle;</span> <span class="text-text-primary">Gap: Design/UX</span> &mdash; you have zero design experience. PMs need to evaluate UX and communicate with designers.<br/>
          <span class="text-text-muted">&ensp;&rarr; Take INFO 214 (User Experience Design) next semester</span>
          <br/><br/>
          <span class="text-yellow-500">&triangle;</span> <span class="text-text-primary">Gap: Business strategy</span> &mdash; no business courses on your resume.<br/>
          <span class="text-text-muted">&ensp;&rarr; Your Finance course helps. Focus on valuation frameworks &mdash; they come up in PM interviews.</span>
          <br/><br/>
          Your NLP + ML foundation is hella solid for AI PM roles. The gaps are fillable in 1&ndash;2 semesters. Fiat Lux! &#128161;
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Demo 2 & 3: Side by side -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 mb-8">

      <!-- Teach mode -->
      <div class="terminal fade-in fade-in-delay-1 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-text-muted font-sans">teach mode</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body space-y-3 text-[13px]">
          <div>
            <span class="text-text-muted">You &rarr;</span>
            <span class="text-text-primary"> Teach me about attention mechanisms</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Think of reading a sentence. When you see &ldquo;it&rdquo; in &ldquo;The cat sat on the mat because it was tired&rdquo; &mdash; your brain looks back to figure out &ldquo;it&rdquo; = &ldquo;the cat.&rdquo; That's attention.
            <br/><br/>
            Quick check: if you have &ldquo;The bank was steep after the rain&rdquo; &mdash; which words would attention focus on to understand &ldquo;bank&rdquo;?
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-text-muted">You &rarr;</span>
            <span class="text-text-primary"> Steep and rain?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-text-secondary">
            Exactly &#128293; &ldquo;Steep&rdquo; and &ldquo;rain&rdquo; tell the model this is a riverbank, not a financial bank.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Course recommendations -->
      <div class="terminal fade-in fade-in-delay-2 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-text-muted font-sans">course advisor</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body space-y-3 text-[13px]">
          <div>
            <span class="text-text-muted">You &rarr;</span>
            <span class="text-text-primary"> What CS courses should I take for AI?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-2.5">
            <div>
              <span class="text-text-primary">CS 182 &mdash; Neural Networks</span> <span class="text-text-muted">(4 units)</span><br/>
              <span class="text-text-muted">Builds directly on CS 188. Deep learning foundations you'll need for AI PM roles.</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-text-primary">CS 285 &mdash; Deep RL</span> <span class="text-text-muted">(3 units)</span><br/>
              <span class="text-text-muted">Hot topic at Anthropic and Google. Strong fit for your career goals.</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-text-primary">INFO 256 &mdash; Applied NLP</span> <span class="text-text-muted">(3 units)</span><br/>
              <span class="text-text-muted">You already have NLP experience from BAIR. iSchool perspective + practical project.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-2">
            &triangle; Fit-based suggestions, not official advising.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Demo 4 & 5: Side by side -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 mb-8">

      <!-- Grades -->
      <div class="terminal fade-in fade-in-delay-1 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-text-muted font-sans">grades</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body space-y-3 text-[13px]">
          <div>
            <span class="text-text-muted">You &rarr;</span>
            <span class="text-text-primary"> What are my grades?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-1">
            <div>Big Data &middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot; B+ <span class="text-text-muted">(88%)</span></div>
            <div>Ethical AI &middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot; A- <span class="text-text-muted">(92%)</span></div>
            <div>Info Law &middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot; A- <span class="text-text-muted">(91%)</span></div>
            <div>NLP &middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot; A&ensp; <span class="text-text-muted">(94%)</span></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-text-muted">You &rarr;</span>
            <span class="text-text-primary"> What do I need for an A in Big Data?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-text-secondary">
            You need <span class="text-text-primary">95%</span> on the final. The final is 40% of your grade.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Campus + Slack -->
      <div class="terminal fade-in fade-in-delay-2 shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-text-muted font-sans">campus &amp; slack</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body space-y-3 text-[13px]">
          <div>
            <span class="text-text-muted">You &rarr;</span>
            <span class="text-text-primary"> What's happening on campus this week?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-1">
            <div>&#128197; EECS Colloquium &mdash; Tue, 4pm, Soda Hall</div>
            <div>&#128197; Data Science Career Fair &mdash; Thu, 10am&ndash;3pm</div>
            <div>&#128197; Noon Concert: Jazz &mdash; Wed, Hertz Hall</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-2">
            <span class="text-text-muted">You &rarr;</span>
            <span class="text-text-primary"> Any updates in the NLP Slack?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-1">
            <div><span class="text-text-muted">#nlp-announcements:</span></div>
            <div>Prof. Bamman: &ldquo;Midterm deadline extended to Apr 4&rdquo;</div>
            <div>TA Sarah: &ldquo;Office hours moved to Wed 3pm&rdquo;</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Demo 6: Telegram alert — centered, narrow -->
    <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
      <div class="terminal fade-in shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-text-muted font-sans">telegram &mdash; automatic alert</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body space-y-2 text-[13px]">
          <div class="text-text-muted text-xs font-sans">3:00 PM &middot; Background heartbeat</div>
          <div class="text-text-secondary mt-2 space-y-1.5">
            <div>&warning; Social Issues writing prompt <span class="text-text-muted">(due TODAY)</span></div>
            <div>&#128203; NLP midterm report <span class="text-text-muted">(due Mar 28, 2d)</span></div>
            <div>&#128200; Ethical AI grade: 92% <span class="text-text-muted">(+3% since yesterday)</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
